{"tid":1305310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎智英會晤美國國家安全顧問博爾頓","createTime":"2019-07-10T23:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:43:09.000Z","uid":41404,"like":548,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"f5814684d483ab4712971211dcf18d56546a8948","tid":1305310,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190711/large/1562785184_fb41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190711%2Flarge%2F1562785184_fb41.jpg&h=b1e531df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英與白宮國家安全顧問博爾頓會面<br />\n正在華盛頓尋求美國政府對香港民主運動支持的香港壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英，周三與美國國家安全顧問博爾頓(John Bolton)會面，討論有關香港及中國的議題。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英跟博爾頓談及反送中抗爭，懇請他盡量以行動支持香港人，並請求美國政府發表言論支持和鼓勵香港的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190711/59810531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59810531&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f1fb48bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59810531&h=6fe5d203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190711/59810531</a>"},{"pid":"4995db8fe161f4f124bb51547ebb03dc2c4feda0","tid":1305310,"uid":50457,"like":320,"dislike":0,"score":320,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:09:20.000Z","msg":"香港外交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215caf69cdd5b624eaed81d1c1378bfece238272","tid":1305310,"uid":152476,"like":140,"dislike":0,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:55:40.000Z","msg":"懇請他盡量以行動支持香港人，並請求美國政府發表言論支持和鼓勵香港的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003a6d5fea60